      "role": "user",
      "content": "we checked the staging areas and the conveyors, nothing there. it's like they're just... gone. it feels almost intentional or like there's some weird glitch in the flow that we just can't see. is there any chance it could be a system error in the handheld scanners or something? like, could a unit get \"lost\" in the software during the handoff?",
